# DISCLAIMER
This is repo / app is NOT officially supported by Security Onion Solutions.

## Overview
AI generated flask app for pulling grid health metrics via the Security Onion Pro API.

## Setup

1. Enable connect api https://docs.securityonion.net/en/2.4/connect.html#enabling-connect-api

2. Give the new api client the following permissions
 - Grid
   - Read
   - Write
 - Nodes
   - Read

3. Download the grids CA cert and leave it named so-ca.crt in this projects root directory.
  - This is available in the 'API clients' menu within SOC.

4. Copy .env_example file to .env and update with client_id / client_secret / url_base values.

5. Build and run the docker container using `./run-it.sh` OR run it using `flask run --host=localhost --port=8080`


